### Get all tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search by title
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?search=assignment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?status=todo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by priority
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?priority=high
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by status and priority
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?status=todo&priority=high
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sort by created date (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?sortBy=created_at&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sort by due date ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?sortBy=due_date&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sort by priority descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?sortBy=priority&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sort by title ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?sortBy=title&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Pagination - Page 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Pagination - Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search + Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?search=assignment&status=todo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search + Sort
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?search=assignment&sortBy=due_date&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Full combination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?search=ass&status=todo&priority=high&sortBy=priority&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}